# 🔮 StartupOracle — AI Startup Success Predictor

A beautiful, dark-themed Streamlit app that uses **Grok-3** to predict whether your startup idea will succeed or fail, based on real statistics and research.

## 🚀 Setup & Run

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Run the app
```bash
streamlit run app.py
```

### 3. Get your Grok API Key
- Visit [console.x.ai](https://console.x.ai)
- Create an account and generate an API key
- Paste it in the app's API key field

---

## 📊 What It Analyzes

| Input | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| Startup Idea | Full description of your product |
| Industry | Sector / vertical |
| Target Market | B2B, B2C, geography |
| Problem & UVP | Core problem and differentiation |
| Business Model | Revenue model |
| Team | Size and founder experience |
| Funding | Stage and capital available |
| Competition | Competitive landscape |
| Moat | Defensibility strategy |
| GTM | Go-to-market approach |

## 📈 Output Scores

- **Success Score** (0–100)
- **1-Year & 5-Year Survival Probability**
- **Market, Team, Timing, Moat Scores**
- **Strengths & Weaknesses** (with research backing)
- **Key Risks**
- **Comparable Successes & Failures**
- **Actionable Advice**
- **Statistical Insight** from CB Insights, Startup Genome, etc.

---

## 🎨 Design

- Dark space theme with purple accents
- Syne + Space Mono typography
- Animated gradients and glassmorphism cards
- Fully responsive